#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.38"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.38:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga "
msgstr "4. Deities "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.38:0.3"
msgid "38. Paṭhamapaṭisambhidāsutta "
msgstr "38. Textual Analysis (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.33, sc1
msgctxt "an7.38:1.1"
msgid "“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nacirasseva catasso paṭisambhidā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with seven qualities will soon realize the four kinds of textual analysis and live having achieved them with their own insight. "

msgctxt "an7.38:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi? "
msgstr "What seven? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
# NOTE: See BB’s note.
msgctxt "an7.38:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘idaṃ me cetaso līnattan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant truly understands: ‘This is mental sluggishness’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:1.4"
msgid "ajjhattaṃ saṅkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘ajjhattaṃ me saṅkhittaṃ cittan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "They truly understand internally constricted mind as ‘internally constricted mind’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:1.5"
msgid "bahiddhā vikkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘bahiddhā me vikkhittaṃ cittan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; "
msgstr "They truly understand externally scattered mind as ‘externally scattered mind’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:1.6"
msgid "tassa viditā vedanā uppajjanti, viditā upaṭṭhahanti, viditā abbhatthaṃ gacchanti; "
msgstr "They know feelings as they arise, as they remain, and as they go away. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:1.7"
msgid "viditā saññā uppajjanti, viditā upaṭṭhahanti, viditā abbhatthaṃ gacchanti; "
msgstr "They know perceptions as they arise, as they remain, and as they go away. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:1.8"
msgid "viditā vitakkā uppajjanti, viditā upaṭṭhahanti, viditā abbhatthaṃ gacchanti; "
msgstr "They know thoughts as they arise, as they remain, and as they go away. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:1.9"
msgid "sappāyāsappāyesu kho panassa dhammesu hīnappaṇītesu kaṇhasukkasappaṭibhāgesu nimittaṃ suggahitaṃ hoti sumanasikataṃ sūpadhāritaṃ suppaṭividdhaṃ paññāya. "
msgstr "The patterns of qualities—suitable or unsuitable, inferior or superior, or those on the side of dark or bright—are properly grasped, attended, borne in mind, and comprehended with wisdom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.38:1.10"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu nacirasseva catasso paṭisambhidā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyā”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these seven qualities will soon realize the four kinds of textual analysis and live having achieved them with their own insight.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.38:1.11"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
